ly in the wake of efforts made at the time of the beijing olympics said many of the government’s efforts to curtail pollution had been offset by the number of construction projects that spit dust into the air and the surge in private car ownership in  ma received the goldman environmental prize in  ma jun became the first chinese social entrepreneur who won the skoll award contents  articles  speeches  list of works  books  see also  references  external links articlesedit ma jun has written for the online journal chinadialogue since  articles are available in chinese and english tackling chinas water crisis online   september  a path to environmental harmony   november  how participation can help chinas ailing environment   january  jun ma  may  the environment needs freedom of information chinadialoguenet retrieved  july   getting involved  may  disaster in taihu lake   june  after green gdp what next   august  tackling pollution at its source   august  ecological civilisation is the way forward   october  your right to know a historic moment  may  ma jun wrote for hong kongs south china morning post from  to  articles are not available for free online green choice apparel supply chain investigation  draft report pdf  p april   speechesedit promoting river protection in china  january  acceptance speech at the skoll award for social entrepreneurship   april  list of worksedit booksedit chinas water crisis chinese title zhongguo shui weiji  see alsoedit china pollution map database environment of china ministry of environmental protection of the peoples republic of china scientific publishing in china  ramon magsaysay award winner referencesedit  a b national geographic explorersma jun accessed   ed norton  time  ma jun time  may   institute of public  environmental affairs china water pollution map  ma jun and naomi li tackling china’s water crisis online chinadialoguenet  september   in china pollution worsens despite new efforts by andrew jacobs with lim xin hui